  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_yanbaopptmerge_SE17.pdf_10_1",
    "text": "Anticipation-A WebApp should be designed so that it anticipates the use's next move.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08750001615924144,
      0.23875661329598566,
      0.8958333373824248,
      0.31414353723156047
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_SE17.pdf_10",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_yanbaopptmerge_SE17.pdf_10_2",
    "text": "Communication-The interface should communicate the status of any activity initiated by the user",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08750003769252186,
      0.3277116395983144,
      0.9041666559185882,
      0.4050925922960245
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_SE17.pdf_10",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_yanbaopptmerge_SE17.pdf_10_3",
    "text": "Consistency-The use of navigation controls, menus, icons, and aesthetics (e.g., color, shape, layout)",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0886628099972674,
      0.4166666671298313,
      0.8401162702062207,
      0.49444444465511267
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_SE17.pdf_10",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_yanbaopptmerge_SE17.pdf_10_4",
    "text": "Controlled autonomy-The interface should facilitate user movement throughout the WebApp, but it should do so in a manner that enforces navigation conventions that have been established for the application.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08749999926292831,
      0.49999999960414665,
      0.8999999854671996,
      0.6223544973984587
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_SE17.pdf_10",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_yanbaopptmerge_SE17.pdf_10_5",
    "text": "Efficiency-The design of the WebApp and its interface should optimize the user's work efficiency, not the efficiency of the Web engineer who designs and builds it or the client-server environment that executes it.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.090116289295096,
